nce  somerset res strategic investors reflect the companys emphasis on both reinsurance experience and capital markets expertise hannover re based in hannover germany is one of the worlds top five reinsurance companies in addition to investing in somerset re hannover re will collaborate with the company to bring comprehensive reinsurance structures to the us life and annuity reinsurance market atlas merchant capital llc was founded to participate in compelling market opportunities in the financial services sector based in new york and london atlas merchant capital was founded by bob diamond and david schamis who together with their partners form a complementary partnership with extensive operating and investing expertise across the financial services landscape further information is available at wwwatlasmerchantcapitalcom atlas is very pleased to bring its partnership and operational focus to help a very talented management team at somerset build a market leading reinsurance business said david schamis founding partner of atlas merchant capital george weiss is the founding shareholder and lead investor in somerset re mr weiss is chairman and ceo of weiss multistrategy advisors llc which has a long history of managing assets for insurance company clients  we are truly fortunate to have a group of investors who have the financial strength capital markets acumen and longterm focus that can help us execute on our growth strategy said kelleher for additional information contact brian holland at bhollandsomersetrecom this press release does not constitute an offer to sell or the solicitation of an offer to buy any security nor shall there be any sale in any jurisdiction in which such an offer solicitation or sale would be unlawful prior to registration or qualification under the securities laws of any such jurisdiction  this release is not an offer to issue or sell insurance or reinsurance and should not be construed as such logo  httpphotosprnewswirecomprnh77logo to view