brand identity following its move from switzerland to bermuda “with completion of this capital raise somerset re is well positioned to serve the needs of the life insurance industry with reliable longterm reinsurance solutions in this persistent low interest rate environment” said pat kelleher the company’s ceo somerset re’s strengths lie in its underwriting and assetliability management expertise said kelleher noting that the average insurance industry tenure of somerset’s leadership team is more than  years “our focus is not on generating deals” kelleher said “we’re focused on creating longterm value for our investors and clients through deep partnerships based on a consultative approach to reinsurance” somerset re said its strategic investors reflect the company’s emphasis on both reinsurance experience and capital markets’ expertise hannover re based in hannover germany is one of the world’s top five reinsurance companies in addition to investing in somerset re hannover re will collaborate with the company to bring comprehensive reinsurance structures to the us life and annuity reinsurance market atlas merchant capital llc was founded to participate in compelling market opportunities in the financial services sector “based in new york and london atlas merchant capital was founded by bob diamond and david schamis who together with their partners form a complementary partnership with extensive operating and investing expertise across the financial services landscape” said somerset re in a statement “atlas is very pleased to bring its partnership and operational focus to help a very talented management team at somerset build a market leading reinsurance business” said david schamis founding partner of atlas merchant capital george weiss is the founding shareholder and lead investor in somerset re weiss is chairman and ceo of weiss multistrategy advisors llc which has a long history of managing assets for insurance company clients “we are truly fortunate to have a group of investors who have the financial strength capital markets acumen and longterm focus that can help us execute on our growth strategy” said kelleher source somerset reinsurance get insurance journal every day subscribe email this print newsletters tweet categories international newstopics atlas merchant capital bermuda bob diamond business moves  mergers david schamis hannover re life and annuity reinsurance life insurance life reinsurance reinsurance reinsurer somerset re somerset reinsurance weiss multistrategy advisors weisshorn re have a hot lead email us at newsdeskinsurancejournalcom advertisers latest comments october   at  am liz saunders says congratulations to george weiss and his team for accomplishing such an unusual and extraordinary launch of this bold new venture see all comments see comments add a comment cancel reply your email address will not be published required fields are marked  name  email  comment notify me of comments via email more newssenate republicans fail in bid to repeal obamacareviewpoint employers rejecting marijuana users will pay a pricefrom here to autonomy morality and retirement timeline for auto insurance prosfederal class action securities fraud filings set historic paceohio’s high court again upholds cities’ use of traffic camerassenate republicans eye ‘skinny’ repeal of obamacaresec commissioner blasts labor department’s fiduciary ruletrump labor department moves to undo obama overtime rulemore news features most popular now this week commented wells fargo insurance accuses failed bidder alliant of poaching executives from here to autonomy morality and retirement timeline for auto insurance pros viewpoint employers rejecting marijuana users will pay a price senate republicans fail in bid to repeal obamacare private insurers cautiously dip toes into florida flood market waters markel to acquire state national for  million progressive unveils online homeowners insurance comparison shopper insurers pummeled by car dealer