am to optimize the benefits for our clients solutions somerset re provides risk management solutions for interest sensitive and capital intensive lines of business      our core strengths include asset management product risk and liability management reinsurance market innovation and transaction design senior team with deep global reinsurance experience our customized transactions allow our clients to release embedded value on inforce noncore lines of business improve long term return on equity improve regulatory and rating agency capital ratios access fresh high quality reinsurance capacity our solutions are ideally suited for interest sensitive life insurance coli  boli products indexed life insurance and annuity products fixed deferred immediate and multiyear guarantee annuities structured settlements   experience our team has deep experience in capital markets actuarial risk modeling reinsurance structuring and investments collectively we have successfully executed hundreds of crossborder reinsurance transactions voltaire is there anyone so wise as to learn by the experience of others chinese proverb to know the road ahead ask someone who has traveled it   somerset re ltd bermuda office     woodbourne avenue pembroke hm  bermuda   patrick kelleher chief executive officer pkellehersomersetrecom brian holland chief marketing officer bhollandsomersetrecom robert reale chief actuary  chief underwriting officer brealesomersetrecom steeve jean chief financial officer sjeansomersetrecom scott selkirk managing director – pricing sselkirksomersetrecom   somerset re ltd swiss branch   dufourstrasse  8 zurich switzerland   thomas conroy chief administrative  compliance officer tconroysomersetrecom stephen gallant chief investment officer sgallantsomersetrecom gerald wigger managing director – investments gwiggersomersetrecom disclosure somerset re is incorporated in bermuda and is licensed and regulated by the bermuda monetary authority the company’s governance activities 